Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.07,0:02:35.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In recent years, there has been a heated debate between the "existence and non-existence" factions
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.62,0:02:40.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But tonight, the controversy over this K. Kazumi will come to an end
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.69,0:02:39.56,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.48,0:02:44.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can the human body really eat that much in one meal? It's incredible
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.31,0:02:49.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If its actually possible, I think they could win the Olympic gold medal in weightlifting
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:58.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After half a year of investigation and tracking, we are finally able to reveal the true identity of the legendary K. Kazumi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.90,0:03:02.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,K. Kazumi-san will be on set soon. \N -Then let's shoot
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.48,0:03:09.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,K. Kazumi's real face is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.24,0:03:14.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Have you heard of such a person?
