Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.12,0:03:18.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I've never heard of them at all \N- I know a little bit about it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.68,0:03:22.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You've heard? \N  -It's a frequent topic of discussion on websites
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.32,0:03:28.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, tonight is the hour of K. Kazumi's reveal
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.46,0:03:30.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You're gonna put an end to it, right?
