Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.16,0:09:47.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't do that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.70,0:09:55.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,On this day, Kazumi came to the guy for her club activity
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:10:02.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After entering the sports warehouse of this arena, I found an old instrument for measuring back muscles
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.22,0:10:08.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The female members half-jokingly measured their back muscle strength values
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:09.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Impossible!  \N-It's only 50
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.86,0:10:13.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is not possible \N-So annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.76,0:10:16.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kazumi is next.  \N-Forget it
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.62,0:10:20.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Try it. \N -Okay, I'll try
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:25.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I tried my best to do it
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.34,0:10:47.60,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's a lie, right?\N  -This is too much
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:50.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Damn it, it's broken, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.54,0:11:00.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The part where the chain is connected to the device started to crack
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:05.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The pointer also stopped working
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.06,0:11:02.75,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This can't be real, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.42,0:11:12.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is not something that humans can do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.96,0:11:15.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The world record is about 500kg
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.22,0:11:18.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you pull off the chain, you probably already have 1t of power
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:22.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Rather than an anomaly, this is more like a monster
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:24.00,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, I think so
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.90,0:11:27.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The next VTR of Kazumi's strange power is
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.27,0:11:29.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm going to the bathroom
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:39.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When I used to travel overseas, after entering a public bathroom
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.24,0:11:53.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.06,0:11:57.40,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's broken
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.00,0:12:05.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I broke the handle and couldn't open the door
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.48,0:12:29.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because of the force, the screw broke
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.21,0:12:39.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The sound of the break echoed in the bathroom, which made me feel embarrassed
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.55,0:12:38.00,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's not embarrassing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.56,0:12:43.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The last example of K. Kazumi's power is
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.72,0:12:49.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When she was a middle school student
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.57,0:12:56.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hey Kazumi, come here for a second
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.38,0:12:59.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? \N -Don't worry about it. Just come here
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.45,0:13:02.00,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Three bad kids
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.58,0:13:10.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When I was in high school, it was a bad high school
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:12.33,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Called over
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.58,0:13:14.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hey Kazumi, let's fight each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.41,0:13:16.00,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:22.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There were many heartless boys who were clamoring to fight me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.22,0:13:28.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Giant! Giant! Giant! Giant! Giant!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.46,0:13:28.44,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.08,0:13:33.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,She's really angry.\N-That's enough
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.80,0:13:36.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I won't lose to someone like this
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:50.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This bad kid, I knocked him out
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.92,0:13:54.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This didn't happen again after high school
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:57.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What the hell
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.12,0:14:00.86,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So cool
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:13:59.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's more
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.12,0:14:04.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you contact me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.84,0:14:06.15,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:13.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,My ex-boyfriend did something that can never be forgiven
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:13.90,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is indeed unforgivable
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.00,0:14:16.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? \N -Kazumi
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.30,0:14:16.59,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really had a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:23.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I found my ex-boyfriend with another girl
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.66,0:14:25.01,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Girls too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.62,0:14:31.84,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Also hit girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:36.49,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Beat both of them up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.62,0:14:37.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When I came back to my senses, I found that I had beaten both of them up
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.97,0:14:39.60,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nonsense
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:49.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,These are the cases of K. Kazumi's strange power
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.98,0:14:48.58,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hmm
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.52,0:14:55.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next, the last of the three characteristics of K. Kazumi
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.73,0:14:58.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,An otherworldly level of appetite
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.83,0:15:00.17,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's right, since has such a huge body
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:07.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,My dinner is about 3 liters of white rice and about 30 plates of curry
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:10.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,21 servings of Udon
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.10,0:15:13.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,3 pots of salad
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.37,0:15:15.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,72 kebab skewers
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.73,0:15:17.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,12 oranges
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.82,0:15:22.00,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,One meal?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.23,0:15:26.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The amount of food is unbelievable, is this amount possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.62,0:15:29.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We invited big eaters to consider it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.84,0:15:33.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And asked them to confirm the amount of food
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.42,0:15:38.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time I want to ask you to confirm the amount of food someone eats at a meal
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.85,0:15:40.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A meal's worth of food? \N -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.01,0:15:48.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's like school dinners
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.97,0:15:52.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is one meal? \N-Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.54,0:15:58.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Probably all three of us together would struggle to finish all of this
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.21,0:16:00.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:06.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If someone can finish this, its not anyone I know
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.17,0:16:10.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine one person able to eat this much
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.09,0:16:17.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Even when I was the reigning champion, I had to fight to adjust my stomach capacity
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.86,0:16:21.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Only then could I eat over 10 kg at a time
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.80,0:16:25.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But you're telling me there's someone that has this much just for dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.42,0:16:29.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It makes me feel like my accomplishments are complete negated
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.42,0:16:36.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Even these big appetite warriors can not handle this amount of food
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:40.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The person who can finish this is called K. Kazumi
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.72,0:16:46.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,K. Kazumi? K. Kazumi? I see
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.12,0:16:48.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I guess she probably can eat this
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.31,0:16:49.54,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:53.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It seems K. Kazumi is well-known in this field
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.92,0:16:58.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sugawara and Angela are both aware of this individual
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.54,0:17:01.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How do you know about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:06.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I searched eating records
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.81,0:17:13.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After looking at everyone's results, I found that one person's record is simply unbeatable
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.52,0:17:14.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I found out in this way
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.42,0:17:23.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At Wagyu Family Restaurant and the buffet soba at Wagyu Noodles Sagami
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:28.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A famous big eater set a record of 24 dishes
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.82,0:17:36.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,K. Kazumi's record is 82, 3.5 times that amount
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.66,0:17:35.02,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's really a record
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.14,0:17:40.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,An official record
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:42.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sugawara knows this person too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.28,0:17:47.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although I know, but, how should I put it say, I don't take it seriously
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:52.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When I was a child, the Loch Ness Monster and Bigfoot
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.02,0:17:54.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,These were popular for a while when I was a child
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.82,0:17:58.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I also categorize K. Kazumi in the same way
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.36,0:18:01.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Like those legends
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:03.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,, Although I think it's good to dream, I still don't believe it
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.23,0:18:09.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In addition, the most powerful food fighter, Kobayashi
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.32,0:18:14.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In the past, K. Kazumi once talked about eating 66 servings of soba noodles
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.77,0:18:18.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Regarding this 0.5kg record, Kobayashi commented
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.13,0:18:25.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They said that after not eating during the day, they ate 66 servings
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.07,0:18:29.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The weight of the soba alone is more than 10kg, its impossible
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.60,0:18:35.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This shows a fundamental misunderstanding of food fighting, its a lie
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.12,0:18:39.69,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.50,0:18:39.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A complete denial of the record
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.67,0:18:47.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But this picture is indeed published on the official website of SAGAMI
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.42,0:18:53.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As a listed company with 255 stores in the group
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:56.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It is hard to imagine that the company would engage in fabrication
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.17,0:19:04.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,K. Kazumi, the mysterious legend, does she exist or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.56,0:19:07.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.53,0:19:22.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.46,0:19:29.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although there's so much info about this, i've never heard of it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.75,0:19:31.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So I wont say anything for the moment
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:34.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We do not have the right to remain silent in this program!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.66,0:19:38.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, I can only say that I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.13,0:19:39.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Do you have any opinion about the strange powers
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.48,0:19:41.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto, you are into fitness
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.73,0:19:47.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This part seems a bit fake
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:50.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But the last part of the soba store
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.42,0:19:52.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That record is not forged, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.54,0:19:54.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are records on the official website
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:59.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In the end, I feel I have to believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:01.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:04.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well, it all seems a little too cartoony
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.19,0:20:08.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But I do hope they exist
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.01,0:20:10.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Today will put an end to it
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.38,0:20:13.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So i'll be a little upset if this person didn't really exist
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.08,0:20:14.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.06,0:20:16.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Its a romantic idea for such a person to exist
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:18.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, I still hope this person really exists
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.57,0:20:23.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, now begins the search for K. Kazumi
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.11,0:20:28.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Does K. Kazumi exist or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.67,0:20:36.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The information so far has been released solely by K. Kazumi herself
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.93,0:20:43.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Of all this information, this record is the only clue to her existence
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.44,0:20:41.57,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Strong evidence
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.74,0:20:51.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So we decided to visit the site of the record
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.32,0:20:55.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,SAGAMI in Higashimurayama, Wagyu Noodle Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.49,0:20:51.32,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,The best way
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.19,0:21:05.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is also a great opportunity to challenge the legendary record
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.68,0:21:13.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In the meantime, we will confirm K. Kazumi's records with the store staff behind the scenes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.40,0:21:21.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Delicious
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.73,0:21:26.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I can eat a lot because i'm super hungry
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.80,0:21:29.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Another, please
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.31,0:21:38.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As expected of one of Japan's top food fights, they swallow soba noodles at high speed
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.11,0:21:40.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How many grams are in this serving?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.82,0:21:44.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,160g per serving \N -It's a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.82,0:21:51.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If the record is true
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.53,0:21:55.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The total weight would be more than 13kg
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.10,0:21:58.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How much can you eat at most?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.00,0:22:01.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Depending on the food, people have different limits
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.14,0:22:05.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I can't eat that much soba
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.27,0:22:07.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It is more difficult for solids like this
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.41,0:22:12.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although I have eaten 8.6kg of soba noodles, but that was a small bowl of soba
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.85,0:22:16.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That was easier to eat so i'm not sure with this one
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.45,0:22:19.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If its just soba, I can probably eat about 8kg at most
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.96,0:22:25.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This bowl has 160g, so 9kg is about 50 servings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.59,0:22:30.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Even if it's a lie, at least tell a lie that is more or less believable, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.33,0:22:34.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The authenticity of this record is currently being confirmed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.69,0:22:38.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, alongside the challenge
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.34,0:22:43.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We asked the store manager, Mr. Mishima, the following questions
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.61,0:22:45.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is this record of 82 servings true?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.98,0:22:49.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This record was before I came to this store
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.89,0:22:53.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I can only check with the head office
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.70,0:22:58.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because there was no staff present at the time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.84,0:23:03.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We asked him to confirm with the head office where the records were left
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.82,0:23:03.83,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really? He really doesn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.40,0:23:07.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A little break
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.35,0:23:14.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At this point, the retired big eater feels he has eaten enough
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.01,0:23:16.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What do you think of 82 servings?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.55,0:23:20.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It must be fake
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.34,0:23:20.36,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This isn't a smoking break!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.36,0:23:22.00,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Definitely not gonna go back and eat more
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.15,0:23:25.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,One hour after the start
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.13,0:23:28.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sugawara and Angela also slow down
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.28,0:23:35.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sorry, about the inquiry with the head office just now
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.80,0:23:40.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sure enough, the head office also gave a definite reply that it is true
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.04,0:23:44.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh, really?  \N-There's no doubt about this record
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.37,0:23:45.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.35,0:23:45.28,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,No doubt \N -Jeez
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.27,0:23:49.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After confirming with SAGAMI head office
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.63,0:23:55.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They confirmed that K. Kazumi's records are factual
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.59,0:23:59.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They said K. Kazumi really ate 82 servings
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.86,0:24:03.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It can't be. Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.56,0:24:06.48,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's a shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.53,0:24:08.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't want to believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.33,0:24:12.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The competitive eating world will be turned upside down \N-For sure
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.00,0:24:15.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Demotivation in the face of such astonishing facts
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.51,0:24:21.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We've now heard their confirmation
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.64,0:24:26.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Until now we just heard some rumors and saw some pictures
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.00,0:24:30.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And yet, I still find it hard to believe
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.29,0:24:37.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The big appetite warriors still cannot accept this unrealistic record
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.76,0:24:44.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After that, Sugawara and Angela continued to eat soba
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.22,0:24:47.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The meal ended with the following results
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.53,0:24:49.03,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not even half of the record
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.62,0:24:52.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Despite being higher than other female competitors in the ranking
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.64,0:24:55.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,K. Kazumi's record is still out of reach
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.77,0:25:00.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Only by combining each are they able to meet the same amount
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.12,0:25:02.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The total amount of three people
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.85,0:25:06.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Its really awful
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.11,0:25:13.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After the location shoot, while greeting the store manager
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.00,0:25:17.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At the Koganei branch of "Aji no Mingei", a subsidiary of our company group
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.40,0:25:20.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,K. Kazumi also has a record there
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.90,0:25:25.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As a result, we received information that K. Kazumi's records were also left in the sister store
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.04,0:25:31.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, we rushed to the location to conduct an interview
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.87,0:25:36.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It is true that there is a 50 udon noodles-serving record left under the name of "Kazu"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.62,0:25:42.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,An oversized record with a total weight of 12kg
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.76,0:25:44.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I didn't actually meet this diner
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.75,0:25:49.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No one here saw her either
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.90,0:25:49.57,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why?\N- No, this is too strange
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.22,0:25:57.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So we sent a request for assistance to the SAGAMI head office, which keeps detailed records
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.91,0:26:02.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In response, we received a reply from the head office
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.58,0:26:05.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Saying they would help find employees who knew about K. Kazumi
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.74,0:26:03.29,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Need help finding it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.89,0:26:08.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So while we waited for a response
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.33,0:26:11.39,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,There must be some, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.78,0:26:14.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We enlisted the help of a detective agency
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.47,0:26:19.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who questioned passersby on streets where there were rumors of sightings
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.73,0:26:22.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Have you heard of K. Kazumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.40,0:26:27.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Tall person, right? Like an urban legend
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.69,0:26:31.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No results were yielded
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.30,0:26:36.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Three weeks after sending an inquiry to SAGAMI head office
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.85,0:26:45.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We received a reply saying that three employees knew about K. Kazumi
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.42,0:26:48.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It would be strange if this were not the case
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.09,0:26:50.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Finally
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.64,0:26:55.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So we rushed to the SAGAMI head office in Nagoya
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.33,0:26:58.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,To meet with one of the individuals in question
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.00,0:27:03.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I am the person
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.44,0:27:08.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is one of the employees who knows K. Kazumi
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.13,0:27:11.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Mr. Imamura, General Manager of SAGAMI Corporation
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.85,0:27:16.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We are hoping to conduct an interview with K. Kazumi
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.55,0:27:21.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is K. Kazumi a real person?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.49,0:27:23.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's true. I've seen her before
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.73,0:27:25.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,She exists!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.53,0:27:29.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is K. Kazumi a real person?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.97,0:27:32.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's true. I've seen her before
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.60,0:27:36.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I've met her before
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.10,0:27:40.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Finally, an eyewitness is found
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.87,0:27:45.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As expected, the legendary K. Kazumi is a real person
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.65,0:27:51.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How were you able to meet K. Kazumi directly?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.19,0:27:57.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Our company has also opened several stores in Bangkok, Thailand
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.96,0:28:05.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,K. Kazumi, as the record holder in Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.37,0:28:07.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We invited her to the opening ceremony of one of our stores there
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.07,0:28:08.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.32,0:28:13.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Mr. Imamura, met her while in Bangkok
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.78,0:28:20.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What was his impression of K. Kazumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.45,0:28:21.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What kind of person is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.68,0:28:28.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I was in charge of the kitchen at the time
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.66,0:28:33.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So basically, I only remember that she was there
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.46,0:28:36.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't know any more details about the situation
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.30,0:28:38.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But for example, she was taller than 2m and so on
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.93,0:28:42.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, really is a super ordinary woman
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.97,0:28:45.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ordinary women?  \N-Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.67,0:28:49.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,2m? Absolutely not, really is completely normal
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.61,0:28:52.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So she's not fat either? \N-No
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.02,0:28:55.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A sudden shocking discovery
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.30,0:28:55.31,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.36,0:29:01.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,K. Kazumi is not a woman with a huge body size of 2m in height and 200kg in weight
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.80,0:29:06.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.06,0:29:10.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, this remarkable witness finally confirms her existence
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.17,0:29:15.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although the amount of food is true, she's actually small?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.97,0:29:17.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is what he says
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.37,0:29:22.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In a sense it's even scarier
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.24,0:29:27.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is anything else a lie, like the frying pan and stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.88,0:29:31.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Its like big Freiza suddenly becoming smaller
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.79,0:29:33.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The final form is unexpectedly small
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.52,0:29:35.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And with deformation, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.46,0:29:37.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Very romantic
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.68,0:29:43.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I suspect that this is a multi-person group calling themselves K. Kazumi
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.73,0:29:48.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Everyone is eating together and keeping up the pretense of this story
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.80,0:29:52.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not one person, that seems likely
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.49,0:29:54.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If this is not the case then it really does not make sense
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.71,0:29:56.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, lets get started
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.41,0:29:59.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who is K. Kazumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.75,0:30:02.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Her face will finally be revealed
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.61,0:30:04.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really? \N -Will we really find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.12,0:30:11.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next we will visit the second person who knows about K. Kazumi
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.29,0:30:14.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's this person
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.65,0:30:20.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At the Higashimurayama store where K. Kazumi left a record
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.14,0:30:24.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Honda, who has been working part-time since the opening of the business
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.91,0:30:27.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We are investigating K. Kazumi
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.84,0:30:30.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Do you know K. Kazumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.45,0:30:33.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although I am a part-time team leader of the night shift
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.28,0:30:42.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Before I heard that during the day someone ate 35 portions of soba
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.12,0:30:46.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,35 servings? \N -Yes, 35 initially
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.66,0:30:49.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I also heard that there were people who could eat very well before
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.63,0:30:54.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,People in the restaurant were talking about 35 servings
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.74,0:30:58.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not quite sure if was due to work
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.12,0:31:00.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But the person gradually started coming here at night too
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.71,0:31:04.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I served her soba noodles once
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.65,0:31:09.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The last time I saw her was about two years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.92,0:31:15.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,She hasn't seen her since the last time she was served two years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.08,0:31:22.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Here we attempt to confirm about the 82 servings
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.10,0:31:25.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Instead of saying she's a big eater
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.70,0:31:29.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As far as I can remember, she was just enjoying the soba noodles
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.27,0:31:34.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is the record of 82 servings real? \N -Yes, it's the soba I served
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.77,0:31:37.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You served it? \N-Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.05,0:31:41.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What was the situation then?  \N-That day she was particularly into it
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.05,0:31:44.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At first she was ordering three servings at a time, then it became five
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.04,0:31:46.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then five at a time, one after another
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.82,0:31:53.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I also remember telling the backroom staff, "I think she's especially into it today, please speed up."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.09,0:31:55.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Isn't the record of 82 servings very impressive?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.30,0:32:00.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, at that time it was unparalleled
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.54,0:32:02.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I have never seen 5 servings of noodles so quickly eaten at once
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.20,0:32:07.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Did they have any leftovers?  \N-No
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.44,0:32:10.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I was going back and forth between the back kitchen and the restaurant endlessly
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.50,0:32:11.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So you've seen how she eats?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.81,0:32:15.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, her eating and asking for more
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.15,0:32:17.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I had to adjust my pace accordingly
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.15,0:32:17.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is how it went
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.95,0:32:22.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Was it a trick or anything?\N  -Not at all
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.54,0:32:26.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Honda witnessed the birth of the record
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.58,0:32:32.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sure enough, the 82 servings is an irrefutable fact
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.96,0:32:32.30,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's incredible
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.37,0:32:38.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There is a rumor online that she is 2m tall
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.87,0:32:41.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, not at all
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.48,0:32:42.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really? \N-Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.78,0:32:46.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What about 170cm? \N -Hm, well, probably
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.98,0:32:51.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This point about her huge physique being untrue is also confirmed
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.50,0:33:01.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The legend of K. Kazumi's is even more mysterious in terms of authenticity
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.06,0:32:58.14,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Only the big appetite is clear
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.12,0:33:06.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The last one who knows K. Kazumi
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.41,0:33:10.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The SAGAMI Tsurunoshima Branch Manager Miyazaki
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.84,0:33:15.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Were you the manager of the Higashimurayama store, when the 82-serving record was set?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.28,0:33:17.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, i've been there for almost 5 years
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.48,0:33:22.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, when the record was set at that time \N -I was there, yes
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.28,0:33:25.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Isn't 82 servings a very impressive record?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.99,0:33:31.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't they get interviewed on TV or in magazines or anything like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.49,0:33:33.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There were interview requests
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.83,0:33:37.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,For K. Kazumi?\N  Yes, for K. Kazumi
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.27,0:33:39.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How were they dealt with?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.20,0:33:46.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I contacted K. Kazumi personally
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.78,0:33:52.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Told her someone wants to interview her
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.31,0:33:55.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Did she reject you?  \N-Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.72,0:34:00.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So you know K. Kazumi's phone number, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.56,0:34:03.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know it
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.77,0:34:10.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Finally, we have found someone who can contact K. Kazumi directly
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.88,0:34:12.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.77,0:34:16.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We really want to meet this person, can you please contact her on our behalf?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.84,0:34:19.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'll try
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.37,0:34:26.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Just say it's a TBS show. We'd really like to meet with her.  \N-Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.45,0:34:25.18,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's right. Don't reveal the name of the show
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.32,0:34:27.92,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please have some confidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.78,0:34:31.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But it seems she doesn't like this type of thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.32,0:34:34.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Making appearances? \N-Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.26,0:34:37.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So it might be a little difficult.  \N-I see
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.09,0:34:43.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After waiting for a week, we received contact from Miyazaki
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.01,0:34:51.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If the conditions for obscuring the face and sound can be met
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.07,0:34:55.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,K. Kazumi is willing to be interviewed
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.54,0:35:00.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So far, she has never accepted a request to appear on TV
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.42,0:35:03.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why did she choose to accept it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.02,0:35:09.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,K. Kazumi will be on set soon \N -Then let's shoot
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.79,0:35:15.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And what about the false claims of being more than 2m in height with strange powers?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.86,0:35:22.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why have fake daily routines been detailed online for 12 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.00,0:35:28.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next, the truth will be revealed
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.22,0:35:49.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The Confessions of K. Kazumi
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.32,0:35:56.41,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Looks very ordinary
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.74,0:36:00.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please take a seat
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.98,0:36:09.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Are you K. Kazumi?\N  -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.92,0:36:12.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We've been searching for K. Kazumi
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.59,0:36:16.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We are honored to meet you.  \N-Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.22,0:36:19.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although there are many questions I would like to ask you
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.09,0:36:24.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Seeing you like this, you don't appear to be 2m tall
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.40,0:36:28.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Did you make that up?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.27,0:36:33.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's a lie. I was stunned when I first heard it myself
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.58,0:36:38.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So it wasn't you who said it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.61,0:36:40.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not me
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.75,0:36:44.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who wrote it?\N  -I don't know. I'd like to know too
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.86,0:36:52.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Shockingly, the account on Yahoo is not operated by the real K. Kazumi
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.84,0:36:54.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's going on here? \N -It's complicated
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.90,0:37:01.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is all the information about K. Kazumi posted on the Internet false?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.87,0:37:04.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's all fake
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.93,0:37:12.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The information about K. Kazumi online is all false, except for SAGAMI's records
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.97,0:37:16.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,None of the information was released by K. Kazumi herself
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.64,0:37:20.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And it is unknown who the perpetrator is
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.56,0:37:26.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How did you see all the information on Yahoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.23,0:37:33.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well, my daughter happened to search for "K. Kazumi" online
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.84,0:37:41.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But it wasn't me that posted it, I didn't even know of the website itself
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.58,0:37:49.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When I saw it, I didn't understand what kind of person was using the name K. Kazumi
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.29,0:37:57.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How did you feel when you first learned that someone was spreading false information?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.33,0:38:00.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Shocked, the image didn't fit me at all
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.90,0:38:04.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I just like soba, that's all
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.24,0:38:08.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's the most impressive thing
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.52,0:38:16.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As K. Kazumi herself has no desire whatsoever to attract the attention of others
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.24,0:38:22.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How did the account talking about her appetite and physique earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.32,0:38:26.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Know about the record that was made later?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.48,0:38:31.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The name seems to have been changed afterwards
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.83,0:38:37.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't mean to offend you, but you are K. Kazumi, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.07,0:38:39.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's me. \N -Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.93,0:38:46.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When I was at SAGAMI, the clerk told me, "Please use your initials to come up with a name"
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.11,0:38:50.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I casually said, "Let's use the name "K. Kazumi"
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.65,0:38:56.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,K. Kazumi is your name, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.92,0:39:00.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Your name is Kazumi, right?\N-Yes, it is
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.18,0:39:09.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At this point, we reconfirmed the details of the record
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.73,0:39:14.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is your record of 82 servings also true?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.44,0:39:17.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's true. \N -That's incredible
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.30,0:39:18.27,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's awesome
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.91,0:39:21.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I just kept eating and ended up having at 82 servings
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.11,0:39:24.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.16,0:39:27.54,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ate and ate until you ate 82?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.45,0:39:30.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When did you start these challenges?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.59,0:39:36.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,About 3 or 4 years ago, only at SAGAMI
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.36,0:39:42.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The more I ate, the more delicious it became, then it ended up as a challenge
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.36,0:39:41.60,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really likes soba
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.06,0:39:46.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Its hard to believe this amount can be eaten just accidentally
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.03,0:39:48.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Did you prepare in anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.37,0:39:55.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I guess I didn't eat much the day before
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.41,0:40:00.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But its true that eating at a buffet isn't great for your health
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.65,0:40:06.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So because of this I don't really do it anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.72,0:40:09.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You mean
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.96,0:40:11.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because it affects your physical condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.59,0:40:13.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Pretty much, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.06,0:40:18.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Now i usually only eat a normal bowl of rice
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.41,0:40:21.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So you usually eat a small or just average amount of food?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.64,0:40:27.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, if I go to a convenience store, I usually just have one or two rice balls
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.01,0:40:33.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What about TV appearances for eating, have you ever received an invitation?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.51,0:40:39.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There were invitations through SAGAMI, but I turned them all down
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.62,0:40:39.88,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,No interest in doing it
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.22,0:40:44.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What about invitations for TV interviews like ours? \N -This is the first time
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.03,0:40:47.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why did you accept our invitation to be interviewed this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.76,0:40:52.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,First of all, I didn't know that K. Kazumi existed before
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.30,0:40:53.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You mean K. Kazumi on the Internet? \N -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.77,0:40:59.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So I didn't expect an interview about this specifically
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.84,0:41:05.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After actually learning about the online situation, that its a fake account
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.51,0:41:11.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Someone's pretending to be me, so I wanted to state its a fake
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.30,0:41:17.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, the K. Kazumi on the Internet is an impostor
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.18,0:41:19.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,To convey this reality
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.90,0:41:25.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,She made up her mind to make a one and only TV appearance
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.50,0:41:27.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you don't mind
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.57,0:41:32.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can you tell us your actual height and weight or foot size?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.81,0:41:40.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Height 167cm Weight about 59 to 60 kg
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.30,0:41:40.08,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Normal
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.01,0:41:42.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The shoe size is 24.5cm
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.32,0:41:44.01,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It is indeed very ordinary
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.85,0:41:50.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The height written on the Internet is 213cm and weight is 222kg \N -Nonsense
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.96,0:41:50.53,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's too much. \N -Why did you tell her that?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.46,0:41:54.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I would also like to ask you about your age range if that's ok
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.16,0:41:57.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Between 55 and 60
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.47,0:42:02.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You are also married, right? You have a daughter?\N  -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.30,0:42:09.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are rumors on the Internet that your husband is a lawyer.\N  -That's not true
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.98,0:42:15.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,K. Kazumi-san, you're not a housewife, but you have a job, right? \N -Yes, I do
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.75,0:42:19.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What do you do for a living?  \N-No comment
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.62,0:42:21.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Apologies
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.02,0:42:29.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Finally, after this program is broadcast, the real situation should be known to the public
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.36,0:42:33.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Do you have any hopes for the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.36,0:42:39.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hopes for the future. On the impostor
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.31,0:42:43.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I hope that the person pretending to be me can bear the corresponding responsibility
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.75,0:42:44.02,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.84,0:42:45.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I hope they disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.11,0:42:51.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,On the existence of K. Kazumi
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.15,0:42:53.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You want it to be over
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.49,0:42:57.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In short, I hope the impostor will disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.16,0:43:04.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That the truth comes to light
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.80,0:43:07.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's all for the interview, thank you. \N -Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.70,0:43:12.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much. Thank you very much.\N  -Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.27,0:43:10.23,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.66,0:43:17.07,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Which way is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.14,0:43:22.05,屏字K,,0,0,0,,{\fad(534,900)}{\1a&H00&\pos(723,726)}{\c&HE2EBFF&\be4\t(454,821,\c&HF3F2F2&\be0)}K. Kazumi just wants a quiet life
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.62,0:43:20.13,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,She came from the right
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.22,0:43:25.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Have you seen this?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.62,0:43:27.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Must've seen this
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.99,0:43:29.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can we take this as a souvenir?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.49,0:43:32.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, I don't want to see that
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.26,0:43:36.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't want to see this
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.37,0:43:38.57,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So who is this? \N -Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.80,0:43:47.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In conclusion, K. Kazumi exists
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.91,0:43:55.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,However, the version online is not the actual person
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.12,0:43:57.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So we don't know who that photo is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.85,0:44:01.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It must be photoshopped
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.29,0:44:04.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Maybe someone was mistaken for K. Kazumi
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.39,0:44:08.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Randomly uploaded a picture and mistaken for K. Kazumi
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.07,0:44:13.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There may be such a person
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.14,0:44:18.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,With this body and strange power
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.01,0:44:21.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's impressive. It's really impressive
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.38,0:44:23.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.  \N-Just agreeing to be in the show is already a big deal
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.41,0:44:31.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,First of all, there really is a woman that can eat that much soba
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.68,0:44:33.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Such a woman exists
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.65,0:44:36.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This urban legend is incredible
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.89,0:44:43.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, especially considering the fact that the professional eaters said its impossible
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.52,0:44:46.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And that she just likes it \N-So she ate and ate and ate
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.74,0:44:48.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Set a record in such a way
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.50,0:44:51.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Its so weird \N-It's awesome
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.42,0:44:55.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's great.\N  -After 82 servings, her health got worse
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.01,0:44:57.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's right. \N -It's horrible, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.01,0:45:04.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In short, we've just watched an hour-long episode about someone that simply loves soba
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.12,0:45:11.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,SAGAMI's soba buffet is available for only 1980 yen
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.66,0:45:15.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Tempura is also available
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.23,0:45:16.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Tempura is very important!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.56,0:45:19.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Only 1980 yen with tempura!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.27,0:45:21.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This was obviously requested
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.31,0:45:21.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A requirement
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.39,0:45:24.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Surely a condition for helping, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.00,0:45:27.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,SAGAMI is not that type of place
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.24,0:45:28.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You have to do what they say
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.21,0:45:30.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate the magnitude of SAGAMI
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.91,0:45:31.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are no conditions attached
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.91,0:45:34.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Our buffet comes with tempura!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.38,0:45:36.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This statement only represents my personal feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.61,0:45:38.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well, then Takahashi, you've eaten it before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.79,0:45:42.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not as of yet, no \N-You haven't!?
